Package: plant
Title: A package for modelling forest trait ecology and evolution
Version: 1.2.1
Author: Daniel Falster [aut, cre], Rich FitzJohn [aut], John Wilshire [ctb]
Authors@R: c(
    person("Daniel", "Falster", , "daniel.falster@unsw.edu.au", c("aut", "cre"), 
